title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 25 2022
description:
Pandemia author Alex Berenson joins C&B and drops a blockbuster: He believes the data shows that vaccination makes you more susceptible to Omicron, and if a new, more dangerous variant emerges, the world could be headed for disaster. Gordon Chang, author of The Coming Collapse of China and The Great U.S.-China Tech War, joins C&B to talk about how China's shutting down to stop covid, the Olympics, and China's role in Ukraine. Clay and Buck review the bombs dropped by Berenson.
